It&#39;s not necessary to use all the above, you can just style the elements you need, eg: just `text`, `number`, and `textarea`:

    input[type=&#39;text&#39;],
    input[type=&#39;number&#39;],
    textarea {
      font-size: 16px;
    }

Alternate solution to have the input elements inherit from a parent style:

    body {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    input[type=&quot;text&quot;] {
      font-size: inherit;
    }

