Below Function converts the Excel sheet (XLSX format) data to JSON. you can add promise to the function. 

    &lt;script src=&quot;https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/xlsx/0.8.0/jszip.js&quot;&gt;&lt;/script&gt;
